pageContext.claim: “You know, when he said that really what he was focused on was trying to be number one in his class at Yale, to me that was so believable. I understand college very well, and I understand being number one in your class, and I understand a lot of things. When he said that, I understood exactly what -- he was so truthful. And I think it came out. I mean, I hope it came out.”
pageContext.analysis: Kavanaugh was not the top of his class in college at Yale University. Yale Law School does not rank students.
